item.title: Do or Die! - Goxenar x Andrew Adams [Brostep/Riddim]
item.dc:creator: anon86704580
item.description:
Love that intro! Builds up so much suspense. Feels like I’m in a Marvel movie. Drop hits HAAARD! I love it! No complaints. Super tight song you guys! Wow! That second drop tho!! Sounds like Spag Heddy and (Old) Skrillex had a baby! Lol

Versatility: 9/10
Creativity: 10/10
Predictability: 9/10
Use of Instruments/Automation: 10/10
Feeling: 10/10

Overall: 48/50 WOW! Probably the highest score I’ve given
